D study visa for more than 3 months of study
Do an internship while you study
Get a post-study work permit
        - Irish general work permit (allows non-EU citizens to work for 2 years once a applicants have a valid job offer)
        - Critical skills employment permit (which included in highly skilled occupation list. This permit makes it easier to get permanent residency ireland for non-eu citizens)
Extend your visa 
        - can extend them upto 3 years (which will make you eligible for Ireland permanent residency for Indian)
Apply for permanent residency in ireland